features: üéß Powerful Pro Audio: High-precision 50mm driver for enhanced sensitivity and clear 3D stereo surround sound; The omnidirectional mic is calibrated to deliver precise, natural-sounding, voice output without unwanted background noise.

üéß Total Wireless Freedom: Play for longer with up to 40 hours of battery life(at 60% volume). 2.4G wireless audio transmission and a 10m range gives you freedom to move. Play in stereo on PS5, PS4,PC and mobile.

üéß Low-Latency Connection: Features low latency 2.4GHz lossless wireless for high fidelity audio, the audio latency is less than 30ms, so you can aim and react even faster because picture and sound are even more synchronized.

üéß Superior Comfort: Flexible design with adjustable headband and soft memory protein foam earpads for a more comfortable experience during long gaming sessions; The cool RGB lighting adds some style to your gaming setup.

üéß Multi-platform Compatibility: No drivers or downloads required, simply Plug & Play, fit for multitude of devices. 2.4G Wireless Mode for PS4, PS5, PC, Switch, mobile devices; Bluetooth mode for Mac, laptop etc..

üéßPlease note: 1.When you connect a PS5/PS4/PC/Laptop, you need to combine the 2-in-1 transmitter before connecting the device; 2.all modes are not compatible with all Xbox devices; 3.the Bluetooth mode is not compatible with the PS4/PS5 console; 4.The microphone is not available when connected to the Switch.
